data.description: Lovely house on a cul-de-sac. A cozy living room featuring a vaulted ceiling. New granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, a newly upgraded refrigerator in 2022, some newer windows, and a new roof in 2023 are just a few of the updates that have been made throughout. Unfinished sub-basement. New furnace and C/A in 2023. Along with a new sliding door that welcomed you to a nice deck on a premium Pond View lot, offer the ideal environment for entertaining or relaxing guests.
